OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry evening but with the
OL,7,Fodd isolated shower possible. Becoming
OL,8,Fdry overnight with clear intervals
OL,9,Fdeveloping near northern coasts.
OL,10,FMostly light easterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mainly dry bright day with
OL,13,Fsome sunny spells breaking through,
OL,14,Fthough there could be a light morning
OL,15,Fshower, and the north coast may stay
OL,16,Fquite cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
